title: Songs that fit the lane experience perfectly
body:
Support: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DIoKr9VDg3A (for what its worth)
mid lane: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DohRa9lsx0Q (stuck in the middle with you)
top lane: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d5ab8BOu4LE (one is the lonliest number) 
jungle: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1tj2zJ2Wvg (welcome to the jungle)
adc: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b6UAYGxiRwU (your so vain)

For the vast majority of these the lyrics flawlessly fit league, often involving someone being ganked or fear of being ganked
